node.text:
during his run through Slate Canyon near Provo. 

Video by @kunkyle

What to do when approached by a cougar?

The DWR states it’s important to know what to do if you ever come in contact with a cougar, especially if you’re an avid hiker or trail runner. They suggest that you: 

- Stop. Never run from a cougar and do not approach the cougar
- Maintain eye contact with the animal 
- Stand up tall
- Do not crouch or squat
- Make yourself look bigger by raising and waving your arms or jacket above your head
- Talk firmly in a loud voice, back away slowly, and leave the area
- Pick up children and pets or keep them very close
- Fight back if you are attacked!
- Protect your head and neck
- Wild Aware Utah also has information detailing how to protect yourself from a cougar. 

Warning for explicit language!

#WildlifePlanet

Coming up for fresh air 🐢⁣ Captured by @thephilwaller these may just be the best turtle headshots we've ever seen 🥰 Tag someone who has to see this!

This is a Green Sea Turtle, named for the green colour of the far under its shell, nothing to do with their outside⁣⁣.

Fun fact: "Turtles can hold their breath up to 30 minutes. I caught this guy getting in a last breath just before the sun set 🌅🐢"

node.text:
Spotting sea snakes with @brodiemoss: “Sea snakes normally avoid humans but this time of year they become very active, sexually frustrated and potentially aggressive as they search for a mate 🐍 like this old fella who appeared from the ocean floor and followed me around on my paddle board before disappearing 😅”

Video by @brodiemoss

#WildlifePlanet

node.text:
Trip To Namibia Competition !

@nuii_icecream_global is giving you the chance to win a 2-week desert elephant adventure to Namibia, Africa and learn first hand about the critically endangered desert elephant population. Expect to get your hands dirty, learn about conservation, make new friends, sleep under the stars and enjoy the natural, beautiful surroundings.

To Enter:
1. Follow @nuii_icecream_global
2. Upload an image to Instagram, tagging @nuii_icecream_global and #MyNuiiAdventure

Winners selection to be judged on originality, quality, unexpected locations and creativity

We can’t wait to see what you guys share.

Competiton ends on 6th September 2021

Good luck!

#MyNuiiAdventure #IceCreamAdventure #AD

T&C’s apply

(This giveaway is not sponsored by Instagram)
